headline: Pinnacle West Beats Q4 Earnings and Sales Estimates, to Invest $8B
summary: PNW tops Q4 earnings and revenue estimates, and plans $7.95B investment through 2028 and reaffirms 2026 EPS outlook.

headline: Will Earnings Beat and a US$65 Billion Plan Reshape Dominion Energy's (D) Growth Narrative?
summary: In February 2026, Dominion Energy reported fourth-quarter 2025 and full-year 2025 results showing higher sales of US$4,093 million for the quarter and US$16.51 billion for the year, with net income rising to US$567 million and US$2.998 billion respectively, alongside 2026 operating earnings guidance of US$3.45–US$3.69 per share.
